analysis.Summary: Vue 3 single-file component that renders an SVG shuffle icon with a configurable fill color.
analysis.Purpose: Provides a reusable shuffle icon for navigation or controls within the application UI.

Components.name: IconShuffle
Components.responsibility: Renders a two-path SVG graphic representing a shuffle symbol, accepts a `fill` prop to control the icon color.

Dependencies: CSS variable --black (used in default fill value)
Notes: No <style> block is defined—styles are entirely inline via SVG attributes.
The `fill` prop default is declared as an object (“{ position: 'rgb(var(--black))' }”) even though its type is String; likely a typo and should be a string value.
Uses script setup syntax from Vue 3.
